feat(integration): IEC 62053 energy metering standard alignment (#79, #70)

Add IEC 62053-21/22 energy metering validation for PoVC attestation:

- integration/metering/iec62053_metering.fl: FastLang circuit validating
  accuracy class (0.2S/0.5S/1.0/2.0), calibration certificates (SE050),
  power factor, power triangle tamper detection
- integration/metering/types.ts: TypeScript types for IEC 62053-21
  (active energy) and IEC 62053-22 (static meters) standards
- circuits/fl/verification_pipeline.fl: ingest_metered_measurement
  circuit accepts IEC 62053-validated telemetry into the existing
  verification flow
- integration/thermogenzero/attestation_adapter.ts: IEC 62053
  metering validation in TZ attestation processing pipeline
- tests/integration/metering/: ESZ test fixtures for accuracy class
  boundary, calibration expiry, tamper detection, power factor

Depends on eStream IEC 62053 circuits (polyquantum/estream-io #145).

Closes #79, closes #70
